Popular film star Yul Edochie has gushed over his daughter, Danielle Yul Edochie. Yul hailed his heir who’ll be a year older soon as the cutest and smartest 17yr old girl in the country, suggesting her marriage may not be too far away. Read also: Why you shouldn’t engage in violence for any candidate – Yul Edochie The father of five captioning his daughter’s photo wrote: “Cutest and smartest 17yr old girl in Nigeria. Head of the table. Danielle Yul-Edochie. Turning 18 soon. Bride price loading.”